Microsoft Certified: Azure Fundementals

Azure Portal Home Screen:
    - Build, manage and monitor everything from simple web apps to complex cloud applications in a single, unified console.
    Features:
        - Personalize: Create your own dashboards, layouts, workflows and colors.
        - Access Control: Fine-grained access control to all your resources. This will make management and governance much easier.
        - Cost Management: Great tooling to keep track of current and projected spend of your Azure resources.
        - One Stop Shop: Single portal, single login for all your Azure assets.
        - Constantly Updated: The portal features and products are constantly updated. Good as you get the latest and greatest. Bad because it can be confusing.
        - Multi-Platform: Portal on Web and various mobile devices.
        
